79b2c2ce-27f1-485f-a661-cda9186dd0b4.title: Note
79b2c2ce-27f1-485f-a661-cda9186dd0b4.text:
this dialogue is for the Elkroy in the maze entrance,
Northwest corner of the maze.

75540054-4402-4137-9776-b8e51225d920.title: Note
75540054-4402-4137-9776-b8e51225d920.text: quick follow interactions, lets for fast teleport

9aaed368-4e42-438d-bd5a-738f6a7189a7.title: Elkoy
9aaed368-4e42-438d-bd5a-738f6a7189a7.text: Hello, welcome to our maze. I'm Elkoy the tree gnome.

98af4802-0f98-4ff4-adcc-50813ec39b82.title: <player>
98af4802-0f98-4ff4-adcc-50813ec39b82.text: I haven't heard of your sort.

092b5d5c-94e3-4c96-be1c-9883443c4499.title: Elkoy
092b5d5c-94e3-4c96-be1c-9883443c4499.text:
There's not many of us left. Once you could find tree
gnomes anywhere in the world, now we hide in small
groups to avoid capture.

2b92e760-0978-4768-bb33-4e8c047ce420.title: Elkoy
2b92e760-0978-4768-bb33-4e8c047ce420.text:
Tree gnomes have been hunted for so called 'fun' since
as long as I can remember.

f18c2790-8352-43be-89ef-adb577c66105.title: Elkoy
f18c2790-8352-43be-89ef-adb577c66105.text:
Our main threat nowadays are General Khazard's
troops. They know no mercy, but are also very dense.
They'll never find their way through our maze.

7f758e5f-ae58-49dd-8324-9e9b444b11ba.title: Elkoy
7f758e5f-ae58-49dd-8324-9e9b444b11ba.text:
The orb, they have the orb. We're doomed.
Do you need me to show you back to the village?

dcf3077c-ab78-4795-ac84-78d879cef553.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

a5a1d8a7-d91f-4d9f-9311-39022cd73580.title: Elkoy
a5a1d8a7-d91f-4d9f-9311-39022cd73580.text: Please help us get our orb back.

2a035c1a-6398-4310-b0d3-16cfee25fde5.title: Note
2a035c1a-6398-4310-b0d3-16cfee25fde5.text:
TELEPORTS YOU TO THE ENTRANCE OF
THE GNOME VILLAGE, WHERE THE SQUEESE THROUGH FENCE 
INTO THE VILLAGE ITSELF IS

80175aad-1d87-425b-9627-ad1766949894.title: Elkoy
80175aad-1d87-425b-9627-ad1766949894.text:
You must retrieve the orb, or the gnome village is
doomed. Do you need me to show you through the
maze?

18d804d2-4fa2-4c06-8b57-13c6b9f8253b.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

64ff033c-730a-4bc5-a190-8314bef74d0c.title: Elkoy
64ff033c-730a-4bc5-a190-8314bef74d0c.text: Please help us get our orb back.

30ca01b3-ec65-4174-9989-7da3291ee050.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

bd605196-acaa-4f3e-98e6-0829e358180f.title: Elkoy
bd605196-acaa-4f3e-98e6-0829e358180f.text:
Here we are. Take the orb to King Bolren, I'm sure
he'll be pleased to see you.

3e626443-f62b-4faf-a34f-6c7bc4325f74.title: Elkoy
3e626443-f62b-4faf-a34f-6c7bc4325f74.text:
You're our saviour. Please return it to the village and
we are all saved. Would you like me to show you the
way to the village?

49e8c932-56ab-496c-9cc3-b7c8386ffcca.title: Elkoy
49e8c932-56ab-496c-9cc3-b7c8386ffcca.text: Please, we must have the orb if we are to survive.

e6c4a54d-1e93-4163-b797-5c172158b5a9.title: Untitled
e6c4a54d-1e93-4163-b797-5c172158b5a9.text:
Please, we must have the orb if we are to survive.
Do you need me to show you through the maze?

43edce9b-f43c-4a5a-b2c5-05b6e6b74469.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

f6cbd40f-aa66-483d-a4e5-878b369934e0.title: Elkoy
f6cbd40f-aa66-483d-a4e5-878b369934e0.text: Please help us get our orb back.

e1874833-1cba-46ce-8db3-3bb6e65a73ed.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

8f0f33f4-3cc9-4c8e-bf82-c583254edc06.title: Elkoy
8f0f33f4-3cc9-4c8e-bf82-c583254edc06.text:
Here we are. Despite what has happened here, I hope
you feel welcome.

e6f03941-ca2e-495c-a194-44f5b88a7831.title: Note
e6f03941-ca2e-495c-a194-44f5b88a7831.text:
TELEPORTS YOU TO THE ENTRANCE OF
THE GNOME VILLAGE, WHERE THE SQUEESE THROUGH FENCE 
INTO THE VILLAGE ITSELF IS

758fe8c2-9173-40b2-9ae2-41a2fc577713.title: Elkoy
758fe8c2-9173-40b2-9ae2-41a2fc577713.text:
Khazard's men have pillaged the village! They
slaughtered many, and took the other orbs in an
attempt to lead us out of the maze. When will the
misery end?

83a30eda-e55b-4660-b946-a31423d82fe1.title: Elkoy
83a30eda-e55b-4660-b946-a31423d82fe1.text: Would you like me to show you the way to the village?

e2af47cc-b92c-42c7-8c2e-910db9fb4ac8.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

7e054495-42fb-497f-8315-120a5b439d16.title: Elkoy
7e054495-42fb-497f-8315-120a5b439d16.text: Here we are. Feel free to have a look around.

0cb3568d-6c51-44fd-a5c4-64ee65ab359c.title: Note
0cb3568d-6c51-44fd-a5c4-64ee65ab359c.text:
TELEPORTS YOU TO THE ENTRANCE OF
THE GNOME VILLAGE, WHERE THE SQUEESE THROUGH FENCE 
INTO THE VILLAGE ITSELF IS

3b4248e8-710f-4720-96d7-5298f93a1918.title: Elkoy
3b4248e8-710f-4720-96d7-5298f93a1918.text:
You saved us by returning the orbs of protection. I'm
humbled and wish you well.

bcc620ee-dab6-4277-80e2-10691f9926ff.title: Elkoy
bcc620ee-dab6-4277-80e2-10691f9926ff.text: Would you like me to show you the way to the village?

13ab5571-a8f7-45a1-bd8b-dd6e97ef2b8a.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

1e510367-f18c-4324-b388-720b43fee3de.title: Elkoy
1e510367-f18c-4324-b388-720b43fee3de.text: Here we are. Feel free to have a look around.

51dff762-3412-4bd1-8cad-c94790510c6c.title: Note
51dff762-3412-4bd1-8cad-c94790510c6c.text:
TELEPORTS YOU TO THE ENTRANCE OF

7855d4e5-41ef-4e98-8066-79d08f34bac5.title: Elkoy
7855d4e5-41ef-4e98-8066-79d08f34bac5.text:
Hi there, I hope life is treating you well. Would you
like me to show you the way to the village?
